    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels or a solid little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s got plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option for someone who doesn\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC. Great as a starter car, a backup runabout, or something to tinker with on the weekends. Priced fairly and ready to go to its next owner.",
