      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid opportunity for someone looking for an affordable driver/project with good bones. This car shows its age cosmetically and is being sold in poor-condition category, but it still offers a strong mechanical foundation and an engaging chassis. Runs and drives, with the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect from a budget-friendly used vehicle. Great candidate for a commuter, weekend wrenching project, or platform to sort and improve over time. Priced to move and leave room for the next owner to make it their own.",
