    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you notice right away\u2014the sort of machine that still turns heads not because it\u2019s perfect, but because it feels real. It\u2019s an ideal fit for someone looking for budget-friendly wheels with personality, a practical runabout, or a rewarding project to make their own. There\u2019s plenty of life and possibility here for the next owner who appreciates value, grit, and the charm of a car with a story to tell.",
      "price": 5900.0,
