      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable, honest transportation with plenty of value for the right buyer. This vehicle offers dependable basic mobility, a comfortable cabin, and a practical layout that makes it a smart low-cost option for commuting, errands, or a starter vehicle. It shows its age and is best suited for someone seeking budget-friendly transportation or a project with potential, but it remains a compelling choice at this price point.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of life left in it? This car isn\u2019t winning beauty contests, but it\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transport, a first project, or a handy spare runaround. It\u2019s priced with its condition in mind, so you\u2019re getting a lot of car for the money. If you\u2019re practical, not precious, and want something affordable you can jump into without breaking the bank, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Clean, straightforward driver with strong project or budget commuter potential. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it has a solid, honest feel and a powertrain that pulls through the rev range without drama. Steering, braking, and chassis response are predictable, making it a usable platform for someone who wants dependable basic transportation or a weekend refresh candidate. A good fit for a buyer who values mechanical simplicity, easy serviceability, and room to improve while driving it as-is. Priced to move for someone who knows what these are worth in today\u2019s market.",
